@startuml
[*] --> InsertCard: card is inserted
InsertCard --> PromptPIN: prompt user to enter PIN
PromptPIN --> VerifyPIN: verify entered PIN against stored information
VerifyPIN --> OptionsProvided: options provided to user if PIN verified successfully
OptionsProvided --> ProcessWithdrawal: process withdrawal request upon user approval
ProcessWithdrawal --> DispenseCash: dispense cash
DispenseCash --> PrintReceipt: print receipt for transaction
PrintReceipt --> ReturnCard: return user's card after completing transaction
ReturnCard --> ResetSystem: reset system and become ready for next user after brief moment

@enduml
